room_title: Escape room "Precinct" by Timed Out in Charlotte
room_address: 12239 N Community House Rd Charlotte, NC 28277
room_description: Three police detectives have disappeared - literally without a trace. There has been no contact with families or friends, no ransom notes, and no evidence of resistance. The chief of police has requested federal help and your team of federal agents has been called in to take point on the investigation. Your only lead: a report of “unusual activity” at a former police station. Can your team unravel the mystery before time runs out for the missing officers?
